# Terms of Service for CraveShift

**Last Updated: 08-12-2025

## 1. Acceptance of Terms

By downloading, installing, or using CraveShift ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the App.

## 2. Description of Service

CraveShift is a mobile application that:
- Analyzes food images to explain craving triggers
- Provides educational information about nutrition and food science
- Offers personalized insights and recommendations
- Tracks your food scanning history

## 3. Subscriptions

### 3.1 Free Tier
- 3 scans per day
- 10 total free scans lifetime
- Limited features

### 3.2 Premium Subscription (CraveShift Pro)
- Unlimited scans
- Unlimited Smart Pairings
- Personalized insights
- Streak protection
- Weekly reports

### 3.3 Pricing
- Monthly: $7.99/month
- Annual: $29.99/year

### 3.4 Billing
- Payment is charged to your Google Play account
- Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled 24 hours before the end of the current period
- You can manage subscriptions in your Google Play account settings

### 3.5 Free Trial
- New subscribers may receive a 7-day free trial
- You will be charged at the end of the trial unless you cancel

### 3.6 Refunds
- Refund requests are handled through Google Play
- We comply with Google Play's refund policies

## 4. User Responsibilities

You agree to:
- Provide accurate information
